dore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前東亞有人賴過野"},{"pid":"6aa10815593920f79ef989a88f411e599e614524","tid":1242442,"uid":62270,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會。佢問返其他銀行借, 一定借比佢。</blockquote><br />\n我唔識呢d野，都係攞定穩陣d"},{"pid":"edbfec33aa15d78db0df08c67b7a7ea7be1193ff","tid":1242442,"uid":227788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6aa10815593920f79ef989a88f411e599e614524","tid":1242442,"uid":62270,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會。佢問返其他銀行借, 一定借比佢。</blockquote><br />\n我唔識呢d野，都係攞定穩陣d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"33bc78dd715640955b7e0692492326040837ed5b","tid":1242442,"uid":257422,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"追究 警察濫權濫用武力 先係我地依家既王牌！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1242366\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1242366</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80f2b59d53fce9869a4459548c7cea75e4ea594","tid":1242442,"uid":57891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"快d 拎錢走"},{"pid":"f81975dd9088b082204dd58f5f9df070d972cb3f","tid":1242442,"uid":83732,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:14:56.000Z","msg":"絕對唔會，只會令到佢拆入資金成本上漲，利息升係因為佢要保持六月半年結嘅存款指標所以提高利率吸錢，retail customers 根本影響唔到大市<br />\n<br />\n利申，想佢收皮"},{"pid":"9cc3f3068867ba30e180b48f183aa6f239015d09","tid":1242442,"uid":170389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9363787862b90023e9895c03cb4246309ceb5a62","tid":1242442,"uid":227788,"like":77,"dislike":4,"score":73,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"唔會。佢問返其他銀行借, 一定借比佢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"借到咁耐就係"},{"pid":"5e281543963d3aff0f91140eabf39c241d9921c9","tid":1242442,"uid":191633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:15:32.000Z","msg":"Citi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Citi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre